data.description: Beautiful 4 bedrooms 2.5 bathrooms, 2-story located in a great Lake Ridge Subdivision. Zoned to excellent Katy Schools. Shorty commute to I-10, 99 Grand Parkway and Highway 6. Minutes to Energy Corridor. 10 commute to Katy Asian town and 15 minutes to Katy Mills Mall. This open concept floor plan that has a spacious living room connect with the kitchen and formal dinning room. 4 bedrooms upstairs plus a large game room. Huge Primary bedroom has recently new laminate wood floor. Recent Roof, Water Heater, HVAC system replaced. Tons of shopping and entertainment nearby. This home is ready for a new owner. Please schedule your showing today!
